description:
Demolition of the existing buildings and structures and erection of a 12-storey building to provide flexible Class E floorspace at ground floor level and 281 student bedrooms and internal and external resident amenity spaces on upper levels, together with refurbishment of the railway arches and the existing 3-storey building fronting onto Holloway Road to provide flexible Class E/E(g) floorspace, a new pedestrian route, landscaping and public realm improvements, disabled car parking, cycle parking and other associated works.

RE-CONSULTATION: THE APPLICATION REPRESENTS A DEPARTURE FROM THE DEVELOPMENT PLAN

open_spaces_details.description: Ground floor public realm. Please refer to Landscaping Statement prepared by Muf.
Roof top student amenity space. Please refer to Landscaping Statement prepared by Muf.
